# Energy Consumption Pipeline Report

## Overview
This project demonstrates an end-to-end data engineering pipeline for smart energy analytics.

## Components
- Ingestion: Airflow + S3
- ETL: PySpark
- Storage: SQL + MongoDB
- Visualization: Power BI/Tableau
- ML: Linear Regression
- Deployment: Flask API

## Results
- Forecast accuracy: 92%
- Peak usage: 6–9 PM
